<div class="content-page wrap fade-in">
  <p class="content-page-eyebrow">About Velour</p>
  <h1 class="content-page-title">More than a blog.<br/><em style="font-style:italic;color:var(--gold)">A craft.</em></h1>
  <p class="content-page-sub">A modern, dynamic blogging platform built with cutting-edge web technologies and designed for serious writers and readers.</p>
  <div class="gold-line"></div>

  <div class="content-section">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>Velour is a platform for sharing ideas, technical tutorials, and insights about web development. We believe in the power of knowledge sharing and community-driven learning.</p>
    <p>Whether you're a developer, tech enthusiast, or someone building the future — you'll find value and inspiration here. Every article is carefully crafted to educate, inspire, and connect.</p>
  </div>

