  <div class="content-section">
    <h2>Key Features</h2>
    <p>Velour supports role-based access with separate admin and user dashboards. Admins have full control over all content, while users can create and manage their own posts.</p>
    <p>The platform includes secure JWT authentication, full CRUD operations for posts, category filtering, real-time search, and a beautifully designed reader experience with dark mode support.</p>
